{
  "** THE KEY HAS BEEN FOUND **": {
    "translation": "钥匙已找到"
  },
  "** KEEP DEFENDING UNTIL THE MAIN ENTRANCE OPEN **": {
    "translation": "坚守防线,等待主入口开启"
  },
  "** FIND A WAY TO OPEN THE ARENA GRATE **": {
    "translation": "想办法打开竞技场铁栅门"
  },
  "[LORE] Long ago, Umbra was a realm of light and wisdom. Now, it lies beneath an eternal dusk. A cursed kingdom devoured by its own shadows.": {
    "translation": "很久以前,安布拉是一片充满光明与智慧的国度.如今此地永陷黄昏,这座受诅咒的王国已被自身的暗影吞噬."
  },
  "** ZOMBIES HAVE REACHED THE OBJECTIVE **": {
    "translation": "僵尸抵达目标点位"
  },
  "** KEEP DEFENDING **": {
    "translation": "坚守防线"
  },
  "** FIND THE KEY TO OPEN THE GRIM ARCHIVE DOOR **": {
    "translation": "寻找钥匙,开启死寂档案馆大门"
  },
  "[LOCATION] GRIM ARCHIVE": {
    "translation": "[区域] 死寂档案馆"
  },
  "** BATTLEFIELD DOOR OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "战场大门将在20秒后开启"
  },
  "** FIND A WAY TO ACCESS THE ARCHIVE **": {
    "translation": "寻找进入档案馆的通路"
  },
  "** WATCH OUT FOR THE METEORS ! **": {
    "translation": "小心陨石!"
  },
  "**ELEVATOR LEAVING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "电梯将在20秒后驶离 "
  },
  "** ACTIVATE 3 LEVERS TO OPEN BOTH PATH **": {
    "translation": "启动三根操纵杆,开启两条通路"
  },
  "** DOORS OPENING IN 15 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "大门将在15秒后开启"
  },
  "** BASTION EXIT GATE OPENING IN 15 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "堡垒出口闸门将在15秒后开启"
  },
  "[LOCATION] SIEGEBOUND COURT": {
    "translation": "[区域] 围城庭院"
  },
  "[LORE] Once a place of strategy and might, now abandoned, the court trembles under the weight of forgotten wars.": {
    "translation": "此地曾是运筹帷幄和彰显强权的重地,如今荒废一片,庭院仍在昔日战乱的重压下震颤."
  },
  "** DOOR OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "大门将在20秒后开启"
  },
  "** BASTION ENTRANCES OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "堡垒各入口将在20秒后开启"
  },
  "[LORE] Shadows coil along the ramparts, hiding the secrets of a kingdom long devoured by darkness.": {
    "translation": "暗影沿着城墙盘绕,藏匿着这座早已被黑暗吞噬的王国的秘密."
  },
  "** SPLIT ON BOTH SIDES **": {
    "translation": "兵分两路防守"
  },
  "** GRIM ARCHIVE ARENA GRATE OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "死寂档案馆竞技场铁栅门将在20秒后开启"
  },
  "** GET INSIDE THE GRIM ARCHIVE ARENA AND KEEP DEFENDING **": {
    "translation": "进入死寂档案馆竞技场并坚守防线"
  },
  "[LORE] Echoes of the Grim Archive awaken something ancient, a protector forged from memory and bone.": {
    "translation": "死寂档案馆的回响唤醒了远古存在,一具由记忆与白骨铸就的守护者."
  },
  "** RESIST 20 MORE SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "再坚守20秒"
  },
  "[LORE] Echoes of the past linger here, whispers of scholars lost to the darkness that consumes this place.": {
    "translation": "过往的残响在此萦绕,皆是葬身这片黑暗的学者们的低语."
  },
  "[LOCATION] CURSED BASTION": {
    "translation": "[区域] 诅咒堡垒"
  },
  "Special thanks to Moltard, Xehanort, Hobbiten, x1aofu, Vndrew, mini, koen, Kaemon, toasty, cron, harley, NiDE, Unloze": {
    "translation": "特别感谢 Moltard、Xehanort、Hobbiten、x1aofu、Vndrew、mini、koen、Kaemon、toasty、cron、harley、NiDE、Unloze",
