  "[LOCATION] UMBRAL DUNGEON": {
    "translation": "[区域] 暗影地牢"
  },
  "[LORE] Beneath the Bastion lies the Umbral Dungeon. A labyrinth drowned in rot and sorrow.": {
    "translation": "堡垒之下便是暗影地牢,一座充斥腐朽与悲恸的迷宫."
  },
  "[LORE] Rusted bars and chained echoes mark the halls where countless souls once screamed.": {
    "translation": "锈蚀铁栏与锁链余响遍布长廊,无数亡魂曾在此哀嚎."
  },
  "** LAKE OF BLOOD DOOR OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
