  "[BOSS] MYCELAR, THE DROWNED GUARDIAN": {
    "translation": "[首领] 迈塞拉尔,溺亡守护者"
  },
  "[LORE] A damp, fungal stench fills the cavern, heralding something monstrous.": {
    "translation": "洞窟中弥漫潮湿菌臭,预示着巨型魔物将至."
  },
  "*** DRAGONLORDS RUINS SECRET MAP FOUND ***": {
    "translation": "找到龙君遗迹秘密地图"
  },
  "[LORE] Scorched ruins mark the passage of two Dragonlords: one of living flame, one of bone and shadow.": {
    "translation": "焦黑遗迹见证两位龙君的过往:一位执掌烈焰,一位统御白骨暗影."
  },
  "[RELIC] A player has collected a dragon relic": {
    "translation": "[遗物] 一名玩家拾取了龙裔遗物"
  },
  "** DRAGONLORDS RUINS AREA UNLOCKED **": {
    "translation": "龙君遗迹区域已解锁"
  },
  "** ALL DRAGON RELICS COLLECTED **": {
    "translation": "全部龙裔遗物收集完毕"
  },
  "[LOCATION] CAVERN OF ECHOES": {
    "translation": "[区域] 回音洞窟"
  },
  "[LORE] Ancient whispers resonate here, telling of those who vanished without a trace.": {
    "translation": "远古低语在此回荡,诉说着那些凭空消失之人的故事."
  },
  "** ZOMBIES DETECTED **": {
