  },
  "** PREPARE TO FIGHT **": {
    "translation": "准备迎战"
  },
  "[LORE] The air reeks of iron and rot, a graveyard unmarked by time.": {
    "translation": "空气中充斥铁锈与腐臭,此处是一座无岁月标记的坟场."
